  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Magic Construct </strong>is an action-survival game where you can <strong>freely edit skills</strong>. Use a simple connection mechanism to freely combine skill modules and build your unique skills.Take on the challenge <i><u>solo</u></i> or team up with <i><u>2-4 players</u></i> to survive and grow stronger in a challenging world.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Customize your experience with <strong>multiple difficulty tags</strong>. The newly added <strong>[Endless Mode]</strong> delivers completely fresh gameplay - where every run brings unexpected surprises and discoveries.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Are you ready to take on the ultimate challenge of magic and survival?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Calm and Composed Combat Experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satisfying Attacks with Status Effects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Variety of Bizarre Creatures</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Skills System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By connecting new nodes, projectiles gain the attributes of those modules</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more nodes you connect, the stronger your projectiles become</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some nodes allow you to adjust their attributes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Difficulty System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each map offers a variety of tags</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each tag corresponds to a specific mechanic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your experience by selecting different tags</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/1b184be4e68cce2a158ff8bef87fbd15.avif?t=1752520599\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras_big/1b184be4e68cce2a158ff8bef87fbd15.avif?t=1752520599 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Achievements System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlocking achievements rewards you with new items, characters, attributes, and more.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/8957d3c9e18f311cd69c531fa0caee95.avif?t=1752520599\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras_big/8957d3c9e18f311cd69c531fa0caee95.avif?t=1752520599 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About Us</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Magic Construct</i> is passionately created by a two-person team. We release updates approximately every two weeks (see in-game \"Update Log\") and will continue optimizing the game experience. Every player's feedback is invaluable to us - we carefully read all reviews and suggestions, and strive to improve in future updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multi-language Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game currently supports 12 languages. Non-Chinese versions use AI translation with manual proofreading.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to language differences, translations may not be perfect. If you find any issues, please contact us via Steam Community or directly - we'll fix them promptly!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Magic Construct </strong>is an action-survival game where you can <strong>freely edit skills</strong>. Use a simple connection mechanism to freely combine skill modules and build your unique skills.Take on the challenge <i><u>solo</u></i> or team up with <i><u>2-4 players</u></i> to survive and grow stronger in a challenging world.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Customize your experience with <strong>multiple difficulty tags</strong>. The newly added <strong>[Endless Mode]</strong> delivers completely fresh gameplay - where every run brings unexpected surprises and discoveries.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Are you ready to take on the ultimate challenge of magic and survival?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Calm and Composed Combat Experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satisfying Attacks with Status Effects</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Variety of Bizarre Creatures</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c8cea486a64dd8d14baa6e9568c52962.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/e77f7784ce0e18ba932a913dcb84557e.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/c3f977c787cb3d83acb7f3fe651c56d2.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Skills System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By connecting new nodes, projectiles gain the attributes of those modules</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more nodes you connect, the stronger your projectiles become</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some nodes allow you to adjust their attributes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.poster.avif?t=1752520599\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.webm?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/a12f17d476304f75ff3fc91cf5b58217.mp4?t=1752520599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Difficulty System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each map offers a variety of tags</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each tag corresponds to a specific mechanic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your experience by selecting different tags</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/1b184be4e68cce2a158ff8bef87fbd15.avif?t=1752520599\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras_big/1b184be4e68cce2a158ff8bef87fbd15.avif?t=1752520599 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Achievements System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlocking achievements rewards you with new items, characters, attributes, and more.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras/8957d3c9e18f311cd69c531fa0caee95.avif?t=1752520599\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176980/extras_big/8957d3c9e18f311cd69c531fa0caee95.avif?t=1752520599 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About Us</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Magic Construct</i> is passionately created by a two-person team. We release updates approximately every two weeks (see in-game \"Update Log\") and will continue optimizing the game experience. Every player's feedback is invaluable to us - we carefully read all reviews and suggestions, and strive to improve in future updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multi-language Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game currently supports 12 languages. Non-Chinese versions use AI translation with manual proofreading.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to language differences, translations may not be perfect. If you find any issues, please contact us via Steam Community or directly - we'll fix them promptly!</p>",
